mple/0521583276WS.pdf Sample], in .PDF form, consisting of the book through page 20.\n* {{cite journal |last=Larsen |first=Alex |date=1905 |title=Photographing Lightning with a Moving Camera |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=00hAQAAIAAJ&pg=PA119#v=twopage&q&f=false |journal=Annual Report Smithsonian Institution |volume=60 |issue=1 |pages=119\u2013127; plates I\u2013VI |ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite news |title=Effects of Lightning |url=http://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/12873 |work=The Mirror of Literature, Amusement, and Instruction |location=Colombia College, New York |volume=12 |issue=323 |date=July 19, 1828 |via=[[Project Gutenberg]] |postscript=. Early lightning research.}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{commons and category|Lightning}}\n{{Wiktionary}}\n*{{cite EB1911|wstitle=Lightning |volume=16 |page=673 |short=x}}\n* [http://science.howstuffworks.com/nature/natural-disasters/lightning.htm How Lightning Works] at [[HowStuffWorks]]\n* {{curlie|Science/Earth_Sciences/Atmospheric_Sciences/Meteorology/Weather_Phenomena/Thunderstorms_and_Lightning|Thunderstorms and Lightning}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20181010173702/https://www.nssl.noaa.gov/research/lightning/ NOAA Lightning research]\n* [http://www.euclid.org/ European Cooperation for Lightning Detection]\n* [http://wwlln.net/ WWLLN] World Wide Lightning Location Network\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150402094547/http://www.lbk.ars.usda.gov/wewc/bof/fulgurites.htm Bibliography of Fulgurites]\n* [http://imgur.com/HMPBICj Image of lightning within a volcanic ash cloud]\n\n{{Meteorological variables}}\n\n{{Atmospheric electricity}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Lightning| ]]\n[[Category:Electric arcs]]\n[[Category:Electrical phenomena]]\n[[Category:Storm]]\n[[Category:Atmospheric electricity]]\n[[Category:Electrical breakdown]]\n[[Category:Space plasmas]]\n[[Category:Weather hazards]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n", "name_user": "176.52.33.86", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "